    <div class="media">
        <h3>Featured Poem</h3>
        <p>Nights may be dark,<br>
        But the moon still shines,<br>
        Casting silver light on distant pines.<br>
        And though the winds may howl and cry,<br>
        The stars remain bold in the sky.</p>
        <p>Things may feel as if they're going wrong,<br>
        But within you, there's a strength so strong.<br>
        Through the storm, you’ll find your way,<br>
        With dawn’s first light, comes a brighter day.</p>
